        "RDF/Turtle distribution of the Labour and Social Policies Ministry ontology for the management of Social Inclusion Pacts - GePI"@en .

<https://w3id.org/italia/labour-social-policies/data/social/distribution/MLPSSOCIAL-RDF-XML> a adms:SemanticAssetDistribution,
        dcat:Distribution,
