        "This is the distribution in RDF/XML of the Labour and Social Policy Ministry Ontology related to the GePi domain defines in a structured and interoperable way the data, relationships, and concepts concerning the management of Social Inclusion Pacts, ensuring semantic uniformity, information integration, and support for the digital processes of the platform, which is an integral part of the Social and Labour Inclusion Information System (SIISL)"@en ;
